localString.value: Even more ferocious and powerful than their lesser kin, these Water Elementals are among the oldest of their kind. A few of the elite amongst them become guardians of the water.

This strange young woman looks at you serenely, her face calm and composed. Her eyes seem alight with the wisdom of ages.
A small altar lay before you. Clearly it is for the offering of gifts to one of the goddess' of this land.
